works.description: Last year, Gebr Heinemann put a 1959 Vintage Porsche up for sale at Hamburg airport. This time, the German travel retailer has teamed up with William Grant & Sons’ Glenfiddich to commemorate the Hamburg Airport’s 100th anniversary. Heinemann is offering 100 bottles of Glenfiddich 1982 through its Duty Free stores. The Glenfiddich 1982 single malt Scotch whisky is part of the Glenfiddich Rare Collection.
